OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThailand moves to legalise 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsame-sex marriage          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thailand has taken a historic step     
OL,6, closer to marriage equality after the  
OL,7, lower house passed a bill giving legal 
OL,8, recognition to same-sex marriage.      
OL,10,FIt still needs approval from the Senate
OL,11,Fand royal endorsement to become law.   
OL,13,FBut it is widely expected to happen by 
OL,14,Fthe end of 2024, making Thailand the   
OL,15,Fonly South East Asian country to       
OL,16,Frecognise same-sex unions.             
OL,18,FIt will cement Thailand's reputation as
OL,19,Fa relative haven for LGBTQ+ couples in 
OL,20,Fa region where such attitudes are rare.
